The Advisory Board is the private advisory of the institute of global transformation.  The meetings with varying advisors are in un-conferencing style focused on forward movement. It has four main routes; share our experiences from our projects, share academic visions, share the vision of senior professionals cross-profiling in areas of expertise and share our ethics. The innovative and strategic planning of future events are held in quartily meetings with the president and 8 nominee counselors on various topics:&#xd;
